===Operation: Clean Sweep===
*[[Battle of Esyram|Dreadnaught ''Warlover'' Attacks Rebel Cargo Operation]]
*[[Battle of Goibniu|Raid on Goibniu Platform]]
*[[Battle of Koensayr 42|Raid on Rebel Factory Koensayr 42]]
